{"tid":1067098,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有香港活地亞倫之稱既殿堂級愛情電影大師兼著名影評人葉念琛新作《阿索的故事》概念海報驚世曝光！！！","createTime":"2019-03-18T09:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T14:26:50.000Z","uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9b03a1abf6c8d5184292c91f36fb636ef3ad6c4e","tid":1067098,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ORbFfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ORbFfb.jpg&h=16dd19fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【阿索的故事 ・ 概念海報】<br />\n<br />\n電影由葉念琛一手包辦監製、導演以及編劇三職，名乎其實，由頭包到落腳嘅葉念琛作品！<br />\n<br />\n葉導演今次揾嚟王菀之，配搭姜皓文、梁漢文同埋蔡潔講述一個情場失意嘅女人仔點樣下決心學揸巴士成為女車長嘅經歷！<br />\n<br />\n電影將於2019年上映，各位觀眾記得密切留意喇！！！<br />\n<br />\n#阿索的故事 2019 #車長報到<br />\n<br />\n好期待葉大導既新作呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6faac086fe1af6ffb579ecef3d5b2819d47f9c","tid":1067098,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:36:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FSi0-alToTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFSi0-alToTA&d=%2FQX5ewQS1riptUQ52WFoKovgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=0ccc0fae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FSi0-alToTA</a><br />\n<br />\n電影故事簡介<br />\n阿索，天生樂觀的中女一名，以當巴士司機為夢想職業。本來與男友程志高拍<br />\n拖七年已到談婚論嫁的時候, 卻發現他在內地竟有小三，唯一的戀情最終泡湯<br />\n。一年後，收到志高喜帖的阿索決定出席婚宴，為舊情作個終極告別禮。<br />\n婚宴當晚，琪琪的前男友李振民原想藉著播放琪琪向他騙財騙色的證據破壞婚<br />\n禮，但如意算盤卻被阿索無心撞破而功虧一簣。事敗後，振民千方百計上門找<br />\n阿索，表示希望阿索配合他的復仇大計。究竟阿索會如何抉擇？會否襯著復仇<br />\n機會來個豬扒大翻新？<br />\n<br />\n#阿索的故事 2019 #車長報到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0da41b0d1682c26e854e5005d3a413ce7236e45","tid":1067098,"uid":36894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:20:42.000Z","msg":"冇stephy有鬼人睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90dfebca4cd9a472d65176706900b28c5695baea","tid":1067098,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"佢啲戲嚟嚟去去都差無幾"},{"pid":"ed91b4765bc972687eb28fb6e0af6a674afe499e","tid":1067098,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:27:09.000Z","msg":"Asok的故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd3314ae4a8079cdc60e23c4965983fe9d3c390","tid":1067098,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T13:28:47.000Z","msg":"見到我討厭政治就唔想睇<br />\n如果唔係,貴為香港活地亞倫,必睇啦"},{"pid":"4fc336353a7855c86b76c3d148b952be1e4b5f33","tid":1067098,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T14:26:50.000Z",